WEBVTT

1
00:00:11.640 --> 00:00:14.970
Very good. All right. Well, welcome along to the Foreign Affairs, Defense, and

2
00:00:15.020 --> 00:00:18.160
Trade Committee. We are very excited to be considering

3
00:00:18.540 --> 00:00:21.140
the India-New Zealand Free Trade Agreement.

4
00:00:21.620 --> 00:00:24.780
